com.motorola.mod

Interface ModDevice.InterfaceInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Parcelable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModDevice.Interface
    Enclosing class:
    ModDevice

    public static interface ModDevice.InterfaceInfo
extends Parcelable
    The static information of a interface within a Moto Mod. This information is statically declared in the manifest and does not guarantee there will be an instance of ModDevice.Interface to be created at runtime.
